    <p class="description">Community spaces on Meta's platform where people with shared interests gather to post, comment, and connect. Unlike Pages, Groups drive <strong>two-way conversation</strong> — and with 1.8 billion monthly active users, they remain one of Facebook's highest-organic-reach features.</p>
